		<div class="question-answer">
			<h2 class="question" id="question"> Where does the opposite needs to stay when the other team is serving? (the opposite is on backcourt)</h2>
			
			<h2 id="explanation">The opposite is usually the best hitter and the worst passer. In consecuence it always has to satay hidden at the back of the court  behind any of the passers from the team, so there is not a position fault.</h2>
		</div>
		
		<div class="answers">
			<div class="answer1" id="answer1">
			
				
				<h3 class = "answer1-text">Passing on the same line as the other passers on the team</h3>
				
			</div>
			
			<div class="answer2" id="answer2">
			
				
				<h3 class = "answer2-text">Opposite is never on backcourt</h3>
				
			</div>
			
			
			<div class="answer3" id="answer3">
				
				
				<h3 class = "answer3-text">Hidden in front of the passers on a corner</h3>
				
			</div>
			
			<div class="answer4" id="answer4">
			
				
				<h3 class = "answer4-text"> Hidden behind the passers</h3>
				
			</div>
		</div>
		
